concurrent_multiset

Interface ConcurrentMultiset<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the elements that can be inserted in the multiset
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FineGrainMultiset, LazyMultiset, LockFreeMultiset

    public interface ConcurrentMultiset<T>
    The interface that defines the methods that each implementation of a concurrent multiset must provide.
    Author:
    Alessandra Fais
